.DT
add_entry
Disk World creator help
add_entry

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_entry -  Add a new entry to the player's database.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int add_entry(object creator,
string player,
string event,
string comment,
mixed * extra)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^source%^RESET%^ - the creator or another object trying to add the event
%^BOLD%^player%^RESET%^ - the name of the player
%^BOLD%^event%^RESET%^ - event the name of the event to be added
%^BOLD%^comment%^RESET%^ - arbitrary comment text (more than one line is OK)
%^BOLD%^extra%^RESET%^ - arbitrary array of arbitrary objects (can be 0)
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
nonzero if the entry was successfully added to the database
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/handlers/playerinfo.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

Add a new entry to the player's database.
.EP

